{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:17:15.928200Z", "created_at": "Wed Mar 10 18:18:41 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-03-10T18:18:41Z", "created_at_ts": 1615400321, "display_name": "Samya Kullab", "handle": "samya_kullab", "id": "1369714340308414465", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 53, \"reply_count\": 2, \"like_count\": 86, \"quote_count\": 4, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "Jasb Aboud Hattab, father of missing activist Ali Jasb, who's quest for justice we documented, was shot dead, prelim investigation shows. \n\nPerpetrators not yet known. \n\nUnlike other families of the missing, Jasb was outspoken, always ready to tell you about his son.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "samya_kullab"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:17:15.928200Z", "created_at": "Wed Mar 10 18:25:59 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-03-10T18:25:59Z", "created_at_ts": 1615400759, "display_name": "Samya Kullab", "handle": "samya_kullab", "id": "1369716175912005643", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 18, \"reply_count\": 1, \"like_count\": 40, \"quote_count\": 0, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[\"Iraq\", \"Iran\"]", "text": "He would often take the six-hour long bus from his rural town in Missan to Baghdad to meet his lawyer.\n\nAlways, he had in hand the documents he hoped would bring to account an Iran-backed militia suspected of kidnapping his son. \n\nAnd always, he spoke of how much he missed Ali.", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "samya_kullab"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:17:15.928200Z", "created_at": "Wed Mar 10 18:30:11 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-03-10T18:30:11Z", "created_at_ts": 1615401011, "display_name": "Samya Kullab", "handle": "samya_kullab", "id": "1369717236424990721", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 37, \"reply_count\": 5, \"like_count\": 83, \"quote_count\": 3, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I remember vividly, we were in the car on the way to meet his lawyer, and I asked him, aren't you afraid?\n\n\"I am afraid...But I lost what was most valuable to me, so I’ve got nothing else to lose.”\n\nThis was our story, I was honoured he let me tell it: https://t.co/FFt6tTGPX4", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[{\"url\": \"https://t.co/FFt6tTGPX4\", \"expanded_url\": \"https://apnews.com/article/virus-outbreak-iraq-iran-archive-3584dcf607d745d4936bc3e4dd4fe030\", \"display_url\": \"apnews.com/article/virus-…\"}]", "username": "samya_kullab"}
