{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Mar 27 14:23:36 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-03-27T14:23:36Z", "created_at_ts": 1616855016, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1375815775408259084", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExffNBEXMAQ1j5D.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 13170, \"reply_count\": 1811, \"like_count\": 100169, \"quote_count\": 1828, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "My 5 yr old boy came home and asked me why bigger kid kept calling him Chinese Boy. My son, confused, told the boy I’m a New Jersey Boy. He laughed it off but my eyes welled up. 50 yrs ago my parents immigrated here but we cannot shake shadow of foreignness. #StopAsianHate THREAD https://t.co/LIgU965ZhO", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Mar 27 14:23:40 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-03-27T14:23:40Z", "created_at_ts": 1616855020, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1375815790088306689", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExfgLXIXIAM8HWn.png\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 560, \"reply_count\": 32, \"like_count\": 7544, \"quote_count\": 43, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "My mom said she would tell me about racism I may face and then follow up with “You are very special. Keep being yourself. You are never alone. Whatever problems come, let us know and we will go through together.” The opposite of feeling foreign is to be loved in a community. 8/13 https://t.co/BQiy81MkLw", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-18T09:36:30.268479Z", "created_at": "Sat Mar 27 14:23:42 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-03-27T14:23:42Z", "created_at_ts": 1616855022, "display_name": "Andy Kim", "handle": "andykimnj", "id": "1375815800469270529", "language": "en", "media_json": "[{\"type\": \"photo\", \"url\": \"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Exfg4p9WEAgKHYr.jpg\", \"alt_text\": null}]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 379, \"reply_count\": 370, \"like_count\": 9593, \"quote_count\": 46, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "I’m going to get ready to have that talk with my son. I’m a bit nervous. He’s such a sweet boy and I don’t know how he will take it. He’s 5 so I won’t go into everything but I think it’s good to get conversation started as they grow up fast. I’ll let you know how it goes. END https://t.co/qKyLFiqmKu", "tweet_type": "reply", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "AndyKimNJ"}
